                                    "score": 1.0,
                                    "content": "Practice Point 1.1.1: Patients with diabetes and chronic kidney disease (CKD) should be treated with a comprehensive strategy to reduce risks of kidney disease progression and cardiovascular disease (Figures 1 and 2).",
                                    "type": "text"
                                }
                            ]
